        "body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Order by 2 PM ET</strong> and we walk or drive your bouquet to your door from the shop on Fort Washington Avenue:</p><ul><li><strong>Washington Heights / Hudson Heights</strong> — 10032, 10033, 10040 (free hand-delivery on foot)</li><li><strong>Inwood / The Cloisters</strong> — 10034 (free hand-delivery)</li><li><strong>Hamilton Heights / West Harlem</strong> — 10031, 10039</li><li><strong>Marble Hill / South Bronx</strong> — 10463, 10468, 10469 (delivery fee +$10)</li></ul><p>Outside these zones? We ship same-day across the five boroughs, or pick Next-Day at checkout (order by 9 PM ET).</p>",
            "type_preset": "paragraph"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["h", "body"],
