          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>Free hand-delivery in Washington Heights, Hudson Heights, and Inwood — every order, no minimum</li><li>Same-day rest of Manhattan — $15 (free over $125)</li><li>Same-day Bronx — $25</li><li>Sympathy / funeral home delivery in upper Manhattan and the Bronx — included on orders over $150</li><li>Saturday delivery — same hours, order by noon</li><li>Sunday — limited; call the shop at (917) 770-1684</li></ul>",
